21:50.434 --> 21:51.644
<i>I mean, this thing</i>
<i>was starting to look</i>

21:51.644 --> 21:54.063
<i>really, really badass.</i>

21:54.063 --> 21:56.732
<i>So now it's just a matter</i>
<i>of getting the blade</i>

21:56.732 --> 22:00.903
where I need it to be
for the actual testing.

22:00.903 --> 22:06.116
‐ Five, four, three,
two, and one.

22:06.116 --> 22:07.618
Bladesmiths,
stop what you're doing.

22:07.618 --> 22:10.412
This second round
of competition is over.

22:10.412 --> 22:13.249
[applause]

22:13.249 --> 22:17.002
