22:21.549 --> 22:23.843
‐ Bladesmiths, welcome
to our strength test:

22:23.843 --> 22:26.053
the ammo can stab and chop.

22:26.053 --> 22:28.848
I'm gonna take each of
your integral knuckledusters,

