22:35.062 --> 22:37.898
<i>I'm feeling pretty nervous,</i>
<i>and I'm feeling anxious.</i>

22:37.898 --> 22:40.025
<i>I'm wanting to see</i>
<i>how it's gonna hold up.</i>

22:40.025 --> 22:41.735
<i>♪ ♪</i>

22:41.735 --> 22:44.738
‐ [grunting]

22:44.738 --> 22:51.704
<i>♪ ♪</i>

22:54.915 --> 22:56.166
‐ All right, Jared.

22:56.166 --> 22:59.253
You do have a lot
of deformation on the edge,

22:59.253 --> 23:00.838
some slight chipping.

23:00.838 --> 23:04.884
The biggest problem I have is,
your handle is so long,

23:04.884 --> 23:07.595
and when I'm getting in here,
