23:07.595 --> 23:09.138
When I'm stabbing,

23:09.138 --> 23:12.099
it's really hurting
the side of my middle finger.

23:12.099 --> 23:14.143
But overall, you survived.
Good job.

23:14.143 --> 23:15.394
‐ Thank you.

23:15.394 --> 23:17.187
‐ Josh, after seeing that,
