23:17.187 --> 23:18.147
‐ I'm ready.

23:18.147 --> 23:19.398
<i>♪ ♪</i>

23:19.398 --> 23:22.318
<i>This is gonna be</i>
<i>a brutal test,</i>

23:22.318 --> 23:25.654
and the nervousness factor
just skyrockets.

23:25.654 --> 23:27.114
<i>♪ ♪</i>

23:27.114 --> 23:30.409
‐ [grunting]

23:30.409 --> 23:37.416
<i>♪ ♪</i>

23:39.627 --> 23:41.795
<i>♪ ♪</i>

23:41.795 --> 23:44.548
‐ All right, Joshua,
from the chopping,

23:44.548 --> 23:47.468
you see you've lost
some pieces of metal.

23:47.468 --> 23:49.845
Puncturing, went through
the steel beautifully.

23:49.845 --> 23:52.848
It took the edge off,
but it's still fairly sharp.

23:52.848 --> 23:56.560
But having my fingers spread
kind of hurt a bit.

23:56.560 --> 23:58.646
Having one of these gone
