24:00.439 --> 24:02.691
but you did open them up
a lot more, so good job there.

24:02.691 --> 24:05.277
‐ Thank you.
‐ Jesse, what are you thinking?

24:05.277 --> 24:06.320
‐ Let's boogie.

24:06.320 --> 24:07.738
<i>♪ ♪</i>

24:07.738 --> 24:10.032
<i>There was a slight</i>
<i>delamination that I caught</i>

24:10.032 --> 24:11.575
<i>and I hopefully eliminated.</i>

24:11.575 --> 24:13.869
<i>If anything is gonna</i>
<i>go wrong with my blade,</i>

24:13.869 --> 24:15.454
<i>it's gonna be</i>
<i>where I forge welded</i>

24:15.454 --> 24:16.705
<i>the two billets together.</i>

