<i>Anything can happen</i>
<i>at that spot,</i>

24:18.457 --> 24:19.833
<i>especially when</i>
<i>you're chopping</i>

24:19.833 --> 24:21.919
<i>or stabbing at something.</i>

24:26.006 --> 24:29.468
‐ [grunting]

24:29.468 --> 24:36.475
<i>♪ ♪</i>

24:41.313 --> 24:42.648
‐ Well, Jesse, you survived.

24:42.648 --> 24:45.025
Stabbed into the can
nice and easy.

24:45.025 --> 24:46.819
I was a little concerned
about this spot up here,

24:46.819 --> 24:48.487
but everything held up.

24:48.487 --> 24:49.905
You got a huge handle.

24:49.905 --> 24:52.825
It didn't hurt my pinkie,
