24:52.825 --> 24:55.035
But held together.
Good job.

24:55.035 --> 24:56.453
‐ Thank you.

24:56.453 --> 24:59.915
<i>♪ ♪</i>

24:59.915 --> 25:02.751
‐ Bladesmiths,
this is the sharpness test.

25:02.751 --> 25:04.670
To find out how sharp
your weapons are,

25:04.670 --> 25:07.423
I will slash across
these sandbags.

25:07.423 --> 25:09.425
I'll also be testing
your knuckledusters

25:09.425 --> 25:11.385
by punching on these sandbags.

25:11.385 --> 25:12.594
Jared, you're up first.
You ready?

25:12.594 --> 25:13.554
‐ Yes, sir.

25:13.554 --> 25:20.602
<i>♪ ♪</i>

25:26.817 --> 25:27.985
‐ All right, Jared.

25:27.985 --> 25:30.946
You have a very stout,
obtuse edge over here,

25:30.946 --> 25:34.450
