30:46.428 --> 30:47.721
I don't want to [bleep]
have to start

30:47.721 --> 30:49.723
this [bleep]damn [bleep]
over again.

30:49.723 --> 30:52.350
<i>I can't afford to lose</i>
<i>any time today,</i>

30:52.350 --> 30:54.102
