<i>I'm running a little</i>
<i>behind today,</i>

30:59.274 --> 31:01.359
<i>so I don't have time</i>
<i>to [bleep] with it too much.</i>

31:01.359 --> 31:03.361
<i>I got to kick it up a notch.</i>

31:03.361 --> 31:05.280
<i>♪ ♪</i>

31:05.280 --> 31:06.740
<i>‐ That extra day would have</i>
<i>come in handy,</i>

31:06.740 --> 31:08.700
but right now,
