<i>The drill bit snaps</i>
<i>in the hole.</i>

32:23.900 --> 32:26.528
<i>There's no way for me to get</i>
<i>this drill bit out of there.</i>

32:26.528 --> 32:28.613
<i>It's emergency time.</i>

32:28.613 --> 32:32.117
<i>♪ ♪</i>

32:32.117 --> 32:35.871
<i>Start a new hole</i>
<i>high on the other side.</i>

32:35.871 --> 32:37.205
<i>There isn't any problem</i>

32:37.205 --> 32:39.583
<i>with leaving</i>
<i>the drill bit in the hole.</i>

32:39.583 --> 32:42.127
<i>But I don't want</i>
<i>to have a messy look.</i>

32:42.127 --> 32:43.211
<i>♪ ♪</i>

32:43.211 --> 32:45.255
‐ Day four,
got a lot of hand work

32:45.255 --> 32:48.091
