lot of hand sanding, polishing,

32:48.091 --> 32:51.595
<i>gluing, so a lot of small,</i>
<i>tedious work today.</i>

32:51.595 --> 32:53.847
8 1/2 pounds.

32:53.847 --> 32:55.515
I'm about 2 1/2 pounds

32:55.515 --> 32:58.643
over what I actually
wanted to have it at.

32:58.643 --> 33:00.145
It's a little bit
more difficult to swing

33:00.145 --> 33:01.313
