<i>that's coming out for rivets.</i>

33:08.153 --> 33:09.821
<i>♪ ♪</i>

33:09.821 --> 33:11.406
<i>I shaved off a good pound,</i>

33:11.406 --> 33:13.825
<i>and it definitely</i>
<i>feels much lighter.</i>

33:13.825 --> 33:16.328
<i>I hope that the weight</i>
<i>isn't the determining factor</i>

33:16.328 --> 33:18.663
<i>when it comes down</i>
<i>to the final judgment.</i>

33:18.663 --> 33:20.999
This challenge was absolutely
a wrecking ball,

